The linear counter has its own INTERNAL halt flag, separate from the length counter's halt flag in the register. Somehow that bit didn't get from my APU doc to the Wiki; it's been added in now.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Wed Mar 11, 2009 5:38 am</p><hr />
